{"about_the_game":"Inspired by real sculpting, Argil is an intuitive VR space that enables quick and effective creation of organic 3D objects, in a peaceful and meditative environment. It offers various easy-to-use tools that feel like manipulating real clay in your own hands. Create seamlessly and quickly anything you want, be it your avatar, a model for 3D printing, a garment, or accessories.<br><br>Designed for a wide range of users, from beginners to professionals alike. This is a perfect tool to learn 3D thinking and realistic sculpting.<br><br>Possibilities include exporting OBJ for 3D-printing, importing other 3D models and manipulating them.<br>The sculpting tools include: push, pull, carve, smooth, add different frequency noise, add/remove resolution, free-draw a mesh in 3D. Other features include: save/load, change and load texture, add different objects (cube, cuboid, sphere, sheet) to the scene, change environment.<br><br>Join our Discord channel to engage in a direct conversation with Argil developers, fellow-users, share artwork, share tutorials and hacks, suggest features, report bugs and more!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1468390/extras/Skull_3_small.png?t=1624987248\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1468390/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1624987248","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1468390/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1624987248","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1468390/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1624987248","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1468390/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1624987248","categories":[{"description":"Tracked Controller Support","id":52},{"description":"VR Only","id":54}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Inspired by real sculpting, Argil is 